videos.description: Houston Astros' Alex Bregman shows off his LSU Tiger spirit by throwing a Houston jersey into the stands, then gives Houston some love by tossing an autograph baseball.
videos.headline: Alex Bregman cheers on LSU

videos.description: Houston's Nate Hinton runs the court, spins, fakes and flips it to Chris Harris Jr. for the dunk.
videos.headline: Harris crushes the rim

videos.description: Daryl Edwards gets the rebound and flips it to Skylar Mays who nails the 3-pointer to give the Tigers a 45-35 lead at halftime.
videos.headline: Mays' 3 gives LSU a 10-point lead going into half

videos.description: Houston's Brison Gresham collects the steal and later Armoni Brooks knocks down the three to cut LSU lead to 53-46.
videos.headline: Houston steal turns into 3

videos.description: With 3:05 left in the game, Armoni Brooks knocks down a corner three to give Houston a 76-72 lead that LSU could not overcome.
videos.headline: Brooks nails dagger 3 for Houston
